                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h5 class="card-title"><h1 class="bold">How it Works</h1></h5>
                      <p class="card-text">The process of registration is easy, the school gives us a call/email we visit the school,
                         we assist in the initial registration of the bus and drivers while training the school personnel. Once a parent is added to the system, they get an email which they use to set up their credentials, then download the app and login. They do not have to add their kids since the school will automatically do that for them. The parents may then decide to add a guardian for the kids(eg, a house help or any other person that they might want to add to the system), When the school starts a trip to pick up or drop-off of the kids, the guardian and the parent will get a notification.
          
                        Parents who would be interested to use the service can also make a formal suggestion to the school, while emailing us and we can pick it from there.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
