              <h5 class="card-title"><h1 class="bold">School Bus Tracking</h1></h5>
              <p class="card-text">The system offers schools with a dashboard to manage vehicle locations trips and route, disable drivers and add new vehicles and drivers.

                In case of distress, the system offers schools with a way to switch the bus ferring student on a certain route, retaining the visibility to the parents/guardians.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-3">
