            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title"><h1 class="bold">Real-Time and Proximity Notification</h1></h5>
              <p class="card-text">The system sends notification to the school management, drivers and parents based on various event. When the student departs from school parent are notified and when the bus is near the designated student drop /pick up zone parent are notified.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
